title: CELEBRATE--listen to the music in the Park!! 1 BR!!
posting_body: ["Close to CHS Field, you can 'round the bases and hit a home in this classic 1 br.--only steps away from Mears Park, CHS field and St Paul's famous Farmer's Market!", ' It features a beautiful Bay Window with fabulous city views.', "You can walk to downtown Saint Paul,check the flowers, the farmer's market and CHS field!", ' Ample storage space, high ceilings, updated lighting, all new appliances, a walk-in closet and versatile living spaces--all combine to make a comfortable home---and FIDO-APPROVED!', 'Get a work out in using our 24/7 private Fitness Center and Studio, relax in our indoor heated pool and get toasty warm in our sauna.', 'Mears Park Place is owned and managed by Bigos Management.', 'Conveniently located in trendy Lowertown across from Mears Park, you can walk the skyway down to the river and bike along the Bike trails through the city parks.', 'We are just 2 blocks from Union Depot and the light rail station, which can take you through St. Paul and connects to Minneapolis and the University campus, as well as the airport.', 'Mears Park Place Apartments features:', '* Indoor Pool', '* Sun Patio', '*', 'Rec Room', '* Sauna', '* Tanning Bed', '* Party Room', '* 24hr gym with fitness studio', '* Underground Parking', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule your guided tour today!', '(Tell them you saw #322 on Craigslist!)', '*Pricing and availability are both determined by requested move-in date, cannot be guaranteed due to on-site leasing activity, and are subject to change at any time.']
